original_title: Dinosaurs: The Official Video of the Natural History Museum
overview: Be prepared to be amazed by the best dinosaur video of all time - from the Natural History Museum, of course. This production uses advanced techniques, pioneered in movies such as Terminator 2 and Jurassic Park, to bring to life the most exciting creatures ever to roam the earth.
tagline: The finest dinosaur video for 65 million years!
title: Dinosaurs: The Official Video of the Natural History Museum
